What better day to shake the table than “Saturday”? Welcome to the Saturday table. Relax and feast your eyes on this delicacy. Photo Primavera kitchen Let’s get real people: Would you invite your ex to your wedding? Some folks are of the belief that one’s Ex is part of one’s past, hence, should remain in the past and not one’s future wedding. However, some of the individuals are open to the idea of their Ex coming to celebrate with them during the wedding ceremony. Others are indifferent about the entire issue. Kindly share your opinion on this Saturday table.